Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸在我小時候因病去世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽一個人把我和姐姐養大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽開心地再婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們搬到了新爸爸的家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他肚子痛 去廁所了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今天開始他就是妳們的新爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是姐姐翔子 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我經常聽說妳的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對弟弟很好的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,翔子 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子真是來得不是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他從小就失去父親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人養大的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,比較小器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠還小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠和翔子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很好的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天開始 這裡就是你們的新家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,房間可以自由使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫我爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好害羞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也許阿誠有點緊張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他一緊張就肚子痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他都是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就能互相瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,能住這麼好的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳同意我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺到很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐最瞭解我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她很溫柔很美麗 總是在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（媽媽再婚後我看到姐姐被強姦\N竟然勃起了 高橋翔子）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就離開了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然後噩夢聞始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,吃飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那我馬上去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是爸爸在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在房間吃可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,去打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,回來也不打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼晚才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸在問你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我和同學去踢球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,踢球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是什麼態度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我讓他不說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜歡踢球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳同意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那現在就不讓他踢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,學習這麼差的笨蛋兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這個時間應該學習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他從小就喜歡踢球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想讓他踢球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是因為誰才能生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,作為姐姐太寵他才會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不過也是因為他媽媽的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說媽媽的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,翔子不要讓爸爸生氣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去換衣服 不然會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\N幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒辦法救姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我看著姐姐衣服濕透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,心情變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快點脫掉 不然會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我說妳這樣會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快點\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不聽爸爸的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要懲罰阿誠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,妳想讓阿誠不能踢球和上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,還不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲也變濕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快點脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不想脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為誰妳才能生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,下面也濕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,父母記錄孩子成長是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只有身體成長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以後爸爸會很嚴厲教育妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐會保護阿誠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸的錢包裡的錢丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,妳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不是妳的話犯人就是阿誠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠不會做這種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這個家裡只有三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,除了阿誠還有誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,還是不讓他讀書了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好教訓他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是我拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好好教育妳們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然偷我的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有拿錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿誠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠怎麼樣也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這種罪犯不能留在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只有身體成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的腦子沒有成長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,淫蕩的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不管阿誠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:16:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管阿誠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠很可憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,放開妳也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妳知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阿誠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老實點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,發育得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,妳來到這裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸就想這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對 誠實點就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很想這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老實了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,果然喜歡這樣色情的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和妳媽媽一樣呢\N不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,身體裡是淫蕩的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,妳知道的
