Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.33,0:47:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.40,0:47:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.34,0:48:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妳似乎有男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.81,0:48:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
